	(36,1,'2014-08-04 16:17:57','2014-08-04 16:17:57','Thanks for stopping by!\r\n\r\nWe would love to hear from you. We are only an email or phone call away. A member of our friendly team will be happy to share additional details or answer any of your questions.\r\n\r\nIf you are looking to join TriLatino, please reach us for more information at <a href=\"mailot:join@trilatino.org\">join@trilatino.org</a>.\r\n\r\nTriLatino members, address any details related to your membership at <a href=\"mailto:members@trilatino.org\">members@trilatino.org</a>.\r\n\r\nFor any other inquiries, including media, sponsorships, and partnerships email us at <a href=\"mailto:info@trilatino.org\">info@trilatino.org</a>.\r\n\r\nIf you rather speak to someone on the phone, ring us at 1-800-TRILATINO. We are available from 10AM-5PM to answer your questions or provide additional information.\r\n\r\nYou can also reach us by mail at:\r\nTriLatino Triathlon Club, Inc.\r\n930 Tiffany Street\r\nBronx, NY 10459\r\n\r\nWe look forward to hearing from you.\r\n\r\nMuvete!\r\nTriLatino','Contact Us','','publish','closed','closed','','contact-us','','','2014-08-04 18:53:44','2014-08-04 18:53:44','',0,'http://spidadesign.us/trilatino/?page_id=36',0,'page','',0),
