	(40,1,'2014-08-04 16:18:22','2014-08-04 16:18:22','As a nonprofit organization, primarily operated through dedicated volunteers, we are always looking for individuals who want to contribute their passion and expertise for a good cause - making sure that everyone gets an opportunity to benefit from affordable training.\r\n\r\nWe are always seeking for help in the areas of marketing, finance, fund development, technology, event planning and recruitment. Should you wish to contribute some time to help, we will ensure that the projects that you work on help you develop your skills and experience in a team environment that fosters innovation and productivity.\r\n\r\nEmail us at <a href=\"mailto:info@trilatino.org\">info@trilatino.org</a> to chat about how you can help us make a difference. Thanks for considering TriLatino as a platform to give back!','Volunteer','','publish','open','open','','volunteer','','','2014-08-04 17:28:21','2014-08-04 17:28:21','',0,'http://spidadesign.us/trilatino/?page_id=40',0,'page','',0),
