	(56,1,'2014-08-04 16:21:55','2014-08-04 16:21:55','<h2>Improve your running form. Go longer and faster.</h2>\r\nWe all run. We run to work, we run for fitness, we run to release stress. No matter what your motivation for running is, now you can improve on that running through proper running techniques that will help you prevent injuries and drills that will make you more efficient. Twice a week we will do interval training and speed workouts to help you increase your distance and ability. Our workouts challenge runners of all abilities, whether you are experienced in the sport or just trying it out for the first time.\r\n\r\n<strong>Running is not just fun, its good for you!</strong>\r\n\r\nAside from releasing tension, sharing a fun moment with friends and earning that hearty meal, there are several health benefits to running such as weight loss, reduced blood cholesterol, strengthening of the bones, reversing the effects of aging and improved cardiovascular and respiratory health. All fine reasons to incorporate running into your active lifestyle.\r\n\r\n<strong>So what are the details around the session?</strong>\r\n\r\nAthletes registered specifically to run training run twice a week as follows:\r\n\r\nLocation, days and time: Both sessions meet at Central Park  Tuesdays meet at 90th Street and 5th Avenue and Thursdays meet at 67th Street and Central Park West. We meet by the benches inside the park at 6:30pm. The session regularly last one hour and there will be bag watch available on location.\r\n\r\nCourse duration: Fifty-four (54) sessions starting March 4 - ending September 4 (no class July 3).\r\n\r\nProgram Cost: Fifty-four sessions for $350* ($6.48 per class).\r\n* Payment plans available\r\n\r\n<strong>At this time we are not registering any more athletes for our spring training session.</strong> For now, we invite you to register for our marathon (or simply running) program. <a title=\"Marathon\" href=\"http://spidadesign.us/trilatino/training/marathon/\">Check out the details</a>.','Run','','publish','open','open','','run','','','2014-08-04 17:45:27','2014-08-04 17:45:27','',0,'http://spidadesign.us/trilatino/?post_type=training&#038;p=56',0,'training','',0),
